title: Never Negotiate with Your Mind
itunes:title: Never Negotiate with Your Mind
description:
Your mind is the thing holding you back. Today I am going to teach you how to work past it.

 

Want to master your mindset? Every Monday I send out an email with mindset tips for the week, click here to receive that email: http://mondayemail.com/
